# Safety & Environment Rules

- Do not execute `aws secretsmanager` from terminal or ad-hoc scripts.
- Default to `dev`; do not modify `recoverysky-iac/src/live/prod` unless the request explicitly says "prod".
- Ensure `AWS_REGION` is set for scripts and deployments.
- Respect `LIVE_HOME`, `PROVISIONING_HOME`, `INFRA_HOME`, and extend `PATH` appropriately.
